data.title: Chung Hwa Middle School, BSB Science Chapter 8 Worksheet: Magnetism
data.meta_description: chap 8 ws - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document contains a 10 question multiple choice quiz and 5 structured questions about magnetism. The multiple choice questions test knowledge about the properties of magnets, including their poles, magnetic fields, uses, and interactions. The structured questions ask students to describe uses of magnets, identify magnetic elements, state properties of magnets, explain observations involving magnet interactions, and draw magnetic field patterns and lines of force. The document provides a worksheet for a middle school science class on the topic of magnetism.
